Install:
claude mcp add zyntra-mail --transport http https://mcp.zyntra.app/mcp

Config:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "zyntra-mail": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "https://mcp.zyntra.app/mcp",
      "headers": {
        "X-API-Key": "YOUR_API_KEY"
      }
    }
  }
}

Usage:
claude mcp add zyntra-mail --transport http https://mcp.zyntra.app/mcp

Then add your API key in Claude settings (see config snippet below).
